WHAT I WOULD GIVE TO SEE
HER SMILE, HEAR HER VOICE
AND HOLD HER TO ME AGAIN

TINA EVANS
23 JAN 1946 - 22 FEB 2017
BEAUTIFUL LOVING HEARTED
WE REMEMBER HER SMILE
HER WARM HEART WITH TEARS
WE THINK OF TINA EACH DAY
I MISS HER MORE THAN
WORDS CAN SAY
LOVE AND HUGS FOREVER
